import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['Date'])]
    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
    sns.lineplot(x='Date', y='CO2', data=data, color='blue')
    plt.title('What is the trend of CO2 concentration over time?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('CO2 Concentration')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.set(style="darkgrid")
    sns.histplot(data=data, x="CO2", kde=True, color="blue")
    plt.axvline(data['CO2'].mean(), color='r', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Mean = {data['CO2'].mean():.2f}")
    plt.axvline(data['CO2'].median(), color='g', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median = {data['CO2'].median():.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45, ha='right')
    plt.title("What is the distribution of CO2 concentration?", wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Year'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['Year'])]
    data['Year'] = data['Year'].dt.year
    avg_co2 = data.groupby('Year')['CO2'].mean().reset_index()
    ax = sns.barplot(x='Year', y='CO2', data=avg_co2, color='blue')
    ax.axhline(y=avg_co2['CO2'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', label='Average CO2 concentration')
    ax.set_xlabel('Year')
    ax.set_ylabel('Average CO2 concentration')
    ax.set_title('What is the average CO2 concentration per year?')
    ax.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from statsmodels.tsa.seasonal import seasonal_decompose

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['Date'])]
    data = data.set_index('Date')
    data = data.resample('M').mean()
    decomposition = seasonal_decompose(data['CO2'], model='additive', period=12)
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 6))
    ax.plot(decomposition.trend, label='Trend')
    ax.plot(decomposition.seasonal, label='Seasonality')
    ax.plot(decomposition.resid, label='Residuals')
    ax.legend(loc='best')
    plt.title('What is the seasonal variation in CO2 concentration?')
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('CO2 Concentration')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```
